{
  "stem": "13471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so there were a lot of ships that had damage to their engine room spaces.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Our damage was all forward.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And therefore, they said, we will send you up to San Francisco and tie you up to a ship and you can supply steam for yourself and for this other ship.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we got to San Francisco on [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] about the end of-- the last half of August of '45, yeah.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, and then we stayed there until VE Day-- or VJ day, it is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the Navy came through, oh, there's no sense of keeping his old hooker in commission any longer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I took up her to Mare Island, and we decommissioned her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mare Island is at the north end of the San Francisco Bay Area, and it's a great Navy installation up there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Has been for a long time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from there, I went back to Washington, and then Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't posted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I still-- I had a lot of leave time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was taking my leave time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- well, on this ship, I had a good friend, [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rouf ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Strau, ?] and we decided-- we'd seen this little ship that the Army had called an FS.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had decided that it would be a good idea to have two or three FS's and work out among the Pacific Islands, taking small amounts of cargo-- principally Copra-- and collect them, and bring them into centers like Singapore, and Manila, and so forth and so on, for transhipment on larger, full-size freighters, you see.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But with this little FS, you see, you'd get into the lagoons-- all right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was to go to Washington and get some of these FS's from surplus.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
